Below is the complete ArgoCD CLI command to create an application with:

âœ” application name
âœ” project name
âœ” sync policy = automatic + prune + self-heal
âœ” source = repo URL, revision (branch), path
âœ” destination = cluster URL + namespace

â¸»

âœ… Full ArgoCD CLI Command

argocd app create <app-name> \
  --project <project-name> \
  --repo https://git.equitasbank.com/<group>/<repo>.git \
  --revision <branch-name> \
  --path <manifest-folder> \
  --dest-server https://kubernetes.default.svc \
  --dest-namespace <namespace> \
  --sync-policy automated \
  --auto-prune \
  --self-heal


