ğŸ” Example (Fully Working)

If your app is spring-api, project is default, repo is â€œdeploymentâ€, branch is at, path is â€œk8sâ€, namespace is springboot-bau:

argocd app create spring-api \
  --project default \
  --repo https://git.equitasbank.com/springboot/services.git \
  --revision at \
  --path k8s \
  --dest-server https://kubernetes.default.svc \
  --dest-namespace springboot-bau \
  --sync-policy automated \
  --auto-prune \
  --self-heal


â¸»

ğŸ§¾ Meaning of Flags

Flag	Description
--project	ArgoCD project (default / custom)
--repo	Git repository URL
--revision	Git branch (e.g., at, preprod, release)
--path	Path where YAML/helm files exist
--dest-server	Kubernetes API URL (use default inside cluster)
--dest-namespace	Target namespace
--sync-policy automated	Enables auto-sync
--auto-prune	Deletes old resources
--self-heal	Fixes drift automatically


